          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Does each location need its own GBP?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Each location has its own GBP, its own NAP, and ranks on its own city queries. theStacc manages every GBP from one dashboard.</div>
