        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does multi-location SEO cost?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">theStacc bills $49 per active location per month. 50 stores cost $2,450 a month. There are no seat fees and no per-user costs. <a href="/pricing/">See pricing →</a></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Will brand voice stay consistent?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Corporate sets one master brand voice. Every store publishes in that voice. City names and neighborhood details swap in per location. No store goes off-brand.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guarantee-section">
    <div class="guarantee-grid">
      <div class="guarantee-card">
        <div class="guarantee-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="guarantee-text"><h4>30-day money-back, per store</h4><p>Not happy with a store's content in 30 days? Refund that store. The chain keeps running.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="guarantee-card">
        <div class="guarantee-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="guarantee-text"><h4>Per-store content lives forever</h4><p>Every article and GBP post stays. Close a store, the content stays on its CMS.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="guarantee-card">
